data.description: Want to love where you live? Are you looking for a move in ready home, that is centrally located? This ranch/rambler style home has been remodeled from top to bottom in the last 3 years. Some updates that have been done; wiring, sheet rock, trim, paint, bathroom update, kitchen update, large amount of flooring, newer appliances, and most of the windows have also been replaced. This home passes St Louis County foster care guidelines and fire marshal guidelines. The wall between the garage and the house was refinished with fire rock. The walk out basement, allows for easy access to the back yard, which is currently partially fenced. A large utility room offers a ton of storage space. There is also an area in the basement, ready to be finished into a 2nd bathroom. Having an attached 2+ stall garage allows for ample storage, with room for your vehicle and toys.
